Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.84,0:23:48.69,DCMain,MAN,0000,0000,0000,,I am Bishamonten.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.83,0:23:52.15,DCMain,POLICE,0000,0000,0000,,It's the woodpecker strategy, Ran-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.66,0:23:54.66,DCItalic,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,One-eyed?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.34,0:23:57.54,DCMain,MAN,0000,0000,0000,,Destroyer of the woodpecker.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.85,0:23:59.54,DCMain,MAN,0000,0000,0000,,You don't know?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.83,0:24:02.54,DCMain,POLICE,0000,0000,0000,,He claims he was forced to shoot.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.84,0:24:06.79,DCItalic,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,Could this person really be...?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.18,0:24:08.78,DCMain,MAN,0000,0000,0000,,A god of war.
